e'>{}</span></p>"},"bv25:28.1":{"pli":"Mahāvilāso tassa jano, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:28.2":{"pli":"siridhammappakāsano; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:28.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṁ tamantarahitaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:28.4":{"pli":"nanu rittā sabbasaṅkhārā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv25:29.1":{"pli":"Koṇāgamano sambuddho, ","html":"<p data-counter='9571'><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:29.2":{"pli":"Pabbatārāmamhi nibbuto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:29.3":{"pli":"Dhātuvitthārikaṁ āsi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv25:29.4":{"pli":"Tesu tesu padesato”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"bv25:30.1":{"pli":"Koṇāgamanassa bhagavato vaṁso tevīsatimo. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"bv26":{"bv26:0.1":{"pli":"Buddhavaṁsa ","html":"<article id='bv26'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li></ul>"},"bv26:0.2":{"pli":"26. Kassapabuddhavaṁsa ","html":"<h1 class='sutta-title'>{}</h1></header>"},"bv26:1.1":{"pli":"“Koṇāgamanassa aparena, ","html":"<blockquote class='gatha'><p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:1.2":{"pli":"Sambuddho dvipaduttamo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:1.3":{"pli":"Kassapo nāma gottena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:1.4":{"pli":"Dhammarājā pabhaṅkaro. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:2.1":{"pli":"Sañchaḍḍitaṁ kulamūlaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:2.2":{"pli":"bahvannapānabhojanaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:2.3":{"pli":"Datvāna yācake dānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:2.4":{"pli":"pūrayitvāna mānasaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:2.5":{"pli":"Usabhova āḷakaṁ bhetvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:2.6":{"pli":"patto sambodhimuttamaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:3.1":{"pli":"Dhammacakkaṁ pavattente, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:3.2":{"pli":"kassape lokanāyake; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:3.3":{"pli":"Vīsakoṭisahassānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:3.4":{"pli":"paṭhamābhisamayo ahu. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:4.1":{"pli":"Catumāsaṁ yadā buddho, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:4.2":{"pli":"loke carati cārikaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:4.3":{"pli":"Dasakoṭisahassānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:4.4":{"pli":"dutiyābhisamayo ahu. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:5.1":{"pli":"Yamakaṁ vikubbanaṁ katvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:5.2":{"pli":"ñāṇadhātuṁ pakittayi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:5.3":{"pli":"Pañcakoṭisahassānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:5.4":{"pli":"tatiyābhisamayo ahu. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:6.1":{"pli":"Sudhammā devapure ramme, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:6.2":{"pli":"tattha dhammaṁ pakittayi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:6.3":{"pli":"Tīṇikoṭisahassānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:6.4":{"pli":"devānaṁ bodhayī jino. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:7.1":{"pli":"Naradevassa yakkhassa, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:7.2":{"pli":"apare dhammadesane; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:7.3":{"pli":"Etesānaṁ abhisamayā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:7.4":{"pli":"gaṇanāto asaṅkhiyā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:8.1":{"pli":"Tassāpi devadevassa, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:8.2":{"pli":"eko āsi samāgamo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:8.3":{"pli":"Khīṇāsavānaṁ vimalānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:8.4":{"pli":"santacittāna tādinaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:9.1":{"pli":"Vīsabhikkhusahassānaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:9.2":{"pli":"tadā āsi samāgamo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:9.3":{"pli":"Atikkantabhavantānaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:9.4":{"pli":"hirisīlena tādinaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:10.1":{"pli":"Ahaṁ tadā māṇavako, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:10.2":{"pli":"jotipāloti vissuto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:10.3":{"pli":"Ajjhāyako mantadharo, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:10.4":{"pli":"tiṇṇaṁ vedāna pāragū. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:11.1":{"pli":"Lakkhaṇe itihāse ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:11.2":{"pli":"sadhamme pāramiṁ gato; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:11.3":{"pli":"Bhūmantalikkhakusalo, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:11.4":{"pli":"katavijjo anāvayo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:12.1":{"pli":"Kassapassa bhagavato, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:12.2":{"pli":"ghaṭīkāro nāmupaṭṭhāko; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:12.3":{"pli":"Sagāravo sappatisso, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:12.4":{"pli":"nibbuto tatiye phale. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:13.1":{"pli":"Ādāya maṁ ghaṭīkāro, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:13.2":{"pli":"upagañchi kassapaṁ jinaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:13.3":{"pli":"Tassa dhammaṁ suṇitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:13.4":{"pli":"pabbajiṁ tassa santike. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:14.1":{"pli":"Āraddhavīriyo hutvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:14.2":{"pli":"vattāvattesu kovido; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:14.3":{"pli":"Na kvaci parihāyāmi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:14.4":{"pli":"pūresiṁ jinasāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:15.1":{"pli":"Yāvatā buddhabhaṇitaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:15.2":{"pli":"navaṅgaṁ jinasāsanaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:15.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṁ pariyāpuṇitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:15.4":{"pli":"sobhayiṁ jinasāsanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:16.1":{"pli":"Mama acchariyaṁ disvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:16.2":{"pli":"sopi buddho viyākari; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:16.3":{"pli":"‘Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:16.4":{"pli":"ayaṁ buddho bhavissati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:17.1":{"pli":"Ahu kapilavhayā rammā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:17.2":{"pli":"nikkhamitvā tathāgato; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:17.3":{"pli":"Padhānaṁ padahitvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:17.4":{"pli":"katvā dukkarakārikaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:18.1":{"pli":"Ajapālarukkhamūle, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:18.2":{"pli":"nisīditvā tathāgato; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:18.3":{"pli":"Tattha pāyāsaṁ paggayha, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:18.4":{"pli":"nerañjaramupehiti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:19.1":{"pli":"Nerañjarāya tīramhi, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:19.2":{"pli":"pāyāsaṁ paribhuñjiya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:19.3":{"pli":"Paṭiyattavaramaggena, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:19.4":{"pli":"bodhimūlamupehiti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:20.1":{"pli":"Tato padakkhiṇaṁ katvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:20.2":{"pli":"bodhimaṇḍaṁ anuttaro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:20.3":{"pli":"Aparājitaṭṭhānamhi, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:20.4":{"pli":"bodhipallaṅkamuttame; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:20.5":{"pli":"Pallaṅkena nisīditvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:20.6":{"pli":"bujjhissati mahāyaso. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:21.1":{"pli":"Imassa janikā mātā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:21.2":{"pli":"māyā nāma bhavissati; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:21.3":{"pli":"Pitā suddhodano nāma, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:21.4":{"pli":"ayaṁ hessati gotamo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:22.1":{"pli":"Anāsavā vītarāgā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:22.2":{"pli":"santacittā samāhitā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:22.3":{"pli":"Kolito upatisso ca, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:22.4":{"pli":"aggā hessanti sāvakā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:22.5":{"pli":"Ānando nāmupaṭṭhāko, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:22.6":{"pli":"upaṭṭhissatimaṁ jinaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:23.1":{"pli":"Khemā uppalavaṇṇā ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:23.2":{"pli":"aggā hessanti sāvikā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:23.3":{"pli":"Anāsavā santacittā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:23.4":{"pli":"vītarāgā samāhitā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:23.5":{"pli":"Bodhi tassa bhagavato, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:23.6":{"pli":"assatthoti pavuccati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:24.1":{"pli":"Citto hatthāḷavako ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:24.2":{"pli":"aggā hessantupaṭṭhakā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:24.3":{"pli":"Nandamātā ca uttarā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:24.4":{"pli":"aggā hessantupaṭṭhikā’. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:25.1":{"pli":"Idaṁ sutvāna vacanaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:25.2":{"pli":"assamassa mahesino; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:25.3":{"pli":"Āmoditā naramarū, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:25.4":{"pli":"buddhabījaṁ kira ayaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:26.1":{"pli":"Ukkuṭṭhisaddā pavattanti, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:26.2":{"pli":"apphoṭenti hasanti ca; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:26.3":{"pli":"Katañjalī namassanti, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:26.4":{"pli":"dasasahassī sadevakā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:27.1":{"pli":"‘Yadimassa lokanāthassa, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:27.2":{"pli":"virajjhissāma sāsanaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:27.3":{"pli":"Anāgatamhi addhāne, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:27.4":{"pli":"hessāma sammukhā imaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:28.1":{"pli":"Yathā manussā nadiṁ tarantā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:28.2":{"pli":"Paṭititthaṁ virajjhiya; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:28.3":{"pli":"Heṭṭhā titthe gahetvāna, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:28.4":{"pli":"Uttaranti mahānadiṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:29.1":{"pli":"Evamevaṁ mayaṁ sabbe, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:29.2":{"pli":"yadi muñcāmimaṁ jinaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:29.3":{"pli":"Anāgatamhi addhāne, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:29.4":{"pli":"hessāma sammukhā imaṁ’. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:30.1":{"pli":"Tassāpi vacanaṁ sutvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:30.2":{"pli":"bhiyyo cittaṁ pasādayiṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:30.3":{"pli":"Uttariṁ vatamadhiṭṭhāsiṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:30.4":{"pli":"dasapāramipūriyā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:31.1":{"pli":"Evamahaṁ saṁsaritvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:31.2":{"pli":"parivajjento anācaraṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:31.3":{"pli":"Dukkarañca kataṁ mayhaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:31.4":{"pli":"bodhiyāyeva kāraṇā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:32.1":{"pli":"Nagaraṁ bārāṇasī nāma, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:32.2":{"pli":"kikī nāmāsi khattiyo; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:32.3":{"pli":"Vasate tattha nagare, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:32.4":{"pli":"sambuddhassa mahākulaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:33.1":{"pli":"Brāhmaṇo brahmadattova, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:33.2":{"pli":"āsi buddhassa so pitā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:33.3":{"pli":"Dhanavatī nāma janikā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:33.4":{"pli":"kassapassa mahesino. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:34.1":{"pli":"Duve vassasahassāni, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:34.2":{"pli":"agāraṁ ajjha so vasi; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:34.3":{"pli":"Haṁso yaso sirinando, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:34.4":{"pli":"tayo pāsādamuttamā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:35.1":{"pli":"Tisoḷasasahassāni, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:35.2":{"pli":"Nāriyo samalaṅkatā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:35.3":{"pli":"Sunandā nāma sā nārī, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:35.4":{"pli":"Vijitaseno nāma atrajo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:36.1":{"pli":"Nimitte caturo disvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:36.2":{"pli":"pāsādenābhinikkhami; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:36.3":{"pli":"Sattāhaṁ padhānacāraṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:36.4":{"pli":"acarī purisuttamo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:37.1":{"pli":"Brahmunā yācito santo, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:37.2":{"pli":"kassapo lokanāyako; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:37.3":{"pli":"Vatti cakkaṁ mahāvīro, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:37.4":{"pli":"migadāye naruttamo. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:38.1":{"pli":"Tisso ca bhāradvājo ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:38.2":{"pli":"ahesuṁ aggasāvakā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:38.3":{"pli":"Sabbamitto nāmupaṭṭhāko, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:38.4":{"pli":"kassapassa mahesino. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:39.1":{"pli":"Anuḷā uruvelā ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:39.2":{"pli":"ahesuṁ aggasāvikā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:39.3":{"pli":"Bodhi tassa bhagavato, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:39.4":{"pli":"nigrodhoti pavuccati. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:40.1":{"pli":"Sumaṅgalo ghaṭikāro ca, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:40.2":{"pli":"ahesuṁ aggupaṭṭhakā; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:40.3":{"pli":"Vicitasenā bhaddā ca, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:40.4":{"pli":"ahesuṁ aggupaṭṭhikā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:41.1":{"pli":"Uccattanena so buddho, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:41.2":{"pli":"vīsatiratanuggato; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:41.3":{"pli":"Vijjulaṭṭhīva ākāse, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:41.4":{"pli":"candova gahapūrito. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:42.1":{"pli":"Vīsativassasahassāni, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:42.2":{"pli":"āyu tassa mahesino; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:42.3":{"pli":"Tāvatā tiṭṭhamāno so, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:42.4":{"pli":"tāresi janataṁ bahuṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:43.1":{"pli":"Dhammataḷākaṁ māpayitvā, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:43.2":{"pli":"sīlaṁ datvā vilepanaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:43.3":{"pli":"Dhammadussaṁ nivāsetvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:43.4":{"pli":"dhammamālaṁ vibhajjiya. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:44.1":{"pli":"Dhammavimalamādāsaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:44.2":{"pli":"ṭhapayitvā mahājane; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:44.3":{"pli":"Keci nibbānaṁ patthentā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:44.4":{"pli":"passantu me alaṅkaraṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:45.1":{"pli":"Sīlakañcukaṁ datvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:45.2":{"pli":"jhānakavacavammitaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:45.3":{"pli":"Dhammacammaṁ pārupitvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:45.4":{"pli":"datvā sannāhamuttamaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:46.1":{"pli":"Satiphalakaṁ datvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:46.2":{"pli":"tikhiṇañāṇakuntimaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:46.3":{"pli":"Dhammakhaggavaraṁ datvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:46.4":{"pli":"sīlasaṁsaggamaddanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:47.1":{"pli":"Tevijjābhūsanaṁ datvāna, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:47.2":{"pli":"āveḷaṁ caturo phale; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:47.3":{"pli":"Chaḷabhiññābharaṇaṁ datvā, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:47.4":{"pli":"dhammapupphapiḷandhanaṁ. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:48.1":{"pli":"Saddhammapaṇḍaracchattaṁ, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:48.2":{"pli":"datvā pāpanivāraṇaṁ; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:48.3":{"pli":"Māpayitvābhayaṁ pupphaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:48.4":{"pli":"nibbuto so sasāvako. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:49.1":{"pli":"Eso hi sammāsambuddho, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:49.2":{"pli":"appameyyo durāsado; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:49.3":{"pli":"Eso hi dhammaratano, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:49.4":{"pli":"svākkhāto ehipassiko. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:50.1":{"pli":"Eso hi saṅgharatano, ","html":"<p><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:50.2":{"pli":"suppaṭipanno anuttaro; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:50.3":{"pli":"Sabbaṁ tamantarahitaṁ, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:50.4":{"pli":"nanu rittā sabbasaṅkhārā. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p>"},"bv26:51.1":{"pli":"Mahākassapo jino satthā, ","html":"<p data-counter='10081'><span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:51.2":{"pli":"Setabyārāmamhi nibbuto; ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:51.3":{"pli":"Tatthevassa jinathūpo, ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span>"},"bv26:51.4":{"pli":"Yojanubbedhamuggato”ti. ","html":"<span class='verse-line'>{}</span></p></blockquote>"},"bv26:52.1":{"pli":"Kassapassa bhagavato vaṁso catuvīsatimo. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}}}